Questions I’d answer now

Tube or pouch?

Prototype both.

Run the exact same gummies in both packages.

Ask customers which they’d buy.

Don’t guess.

⸻

60 gummies?

I’d start with:

60 gummies (30 servings)

That matches what consumers already expect from many gummy supplements and gives a full month’s supply at two gummies per serving.

⸻

Matte or glossy?

Matte.

Looks significantly more premium.

⸻

Child resistant?

Not for Version 1 unless your formulation or regulations require it. Simpler closures reduce cost and friction. Confirm requirements with your manufacturer and regulatory consultant.

⸻

Flavor first?

Absolutely.

Nobody buys a second bottle because of the logo.

Everyone buys a second bottle because it tastes good and works.

